''Embarrassment of Riches'' is an 6-song "albumette" by [[Elephant Micah]] scheduled to be released in late summer [[2006]] on Micah's own [[LRRC (Luddite Rural Recording Cooperative)|LRRC]] label. No details about the tracklist are yet known.

